alpine.name: alpine
alpine.version-variable:
ALPINE_VERSION
# For alpine we should not use subfolders

grav.name: grav
grav.version-variable:
PHP_VERSION
    && docker-php-ext-install opcache \
    && docker-php-ext-configure intl \
    && docker-php-ext-install intl \
    && docker-php-ext-configure gd --with-freetype --with-jpeg \
    && docker-php-ext-install -j$(nproc) gd \
    && docker-php-ext-install zip \
//secure.php.net/manual/en/opcache.installation.php
    echo 'expose_php=off'; \
     > /usr/local/etc/php/conf.d/php-recommended.ini
    && docker-php-ext-enable apcu yaml
RUN (crontab -l; echo "* * * * * cd /var/www/html;/usr/local/bin/php bin/grav scheduler 1>> /dev/null 2>&1") | crontab -

bitnami-grafana.name: bitnami-grafana
bitnami-grafana.version-variable:
BITNAMI_GRAFANA_VERSION
ADD setup.sh /opt/bitnami/grafana/setup.sh
RUN /opt/bitnami/grafana/setup.sh
COPY --from=dashboards /dashboards /opt/bitnami/grafana/dashboard-sets
# COPY --from=mqtt_datasource_build /mqtt-datasource/ /opt/bitnami/grafana/data/plugins/mqtt-datasource
1001 /opt/bitnami/grafana/data /opt/bitnami/grafana/logs
